{"tid":1280257,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梅乙己是沒拿過國家杯而稱球王的唯一的人","createTime":"2019-07-03T02:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:28:48.000Z","uid":25345,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9ade3eb1076a99e56d3506f828086bbfb6d5a8c2","tid":1280257,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:16:14.000Z","msg":"梅乙己是沒拿過國家杯而稱球王的唯一的人。他身材不算高大；青白臉色，皺紋間時常夾些傷痕；一大堆亂蓬蓬的紋身。雖然打過生長激素，可是又挫又矮，似乎十多歲後就沒有長高。 他對人說話，總是滿口阿根廷要奪冠，教人半懂不懂的。 梅乙己一到國家隊，所有看球的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，&ldquo;梅乙己，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！&rdquo; 他不回答，對櫃裡說&ldquo;再舉辦一次美洲杯，要103周年紀念版的。&rdquo;便排出九文大錢。 他們又故意的高聲嚷道，&ldquo;你一定又輸球了！&rdquo; 梅乙己睜大眼睛說，&ldquo;你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo; &ldquo;什麼清白？我親眼見你決賽把點球踢到天上去。&rdquo; 梅乙己便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，&ldquo;百年美洲杯不能算輸&hellip;&hellip;百年&hellip;&hellip;友誼賽性質的賽事，能算輸麼？&rdquo; 接連便是難懂的話，什麼&ldquo;世界杯金球&rdquo;，什麼&ldquo;我沒偷稅&rdquo;之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來，整個球迷區充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"4e1de783ffdf6a3f1f09be22d493b33b2e06b067","tid":1280257,"uid":54551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"@王騎"},{"pid":"f5d852f9a58df82dd3be57cf8045dccd90f4f505","tid":1280257,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a61675ce8276607a11b64974275b5fde71fc0f","tid":1280257,"uid":14910,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4588ccb3a3e0acaea7f9c331f194be723b9264e9","tid":1280257,"uid":90479,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo; &ldquo;什麼清白？我親眼見你決賽把點球踢到天上去。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eef6c61ea7952983e5adfa8afe50e5ddf704bd","tid":1280257,"uid":33660,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"再舉辦一次美洲杯，要103周年紀念版的。<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢句笑撚左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1ef9799fd85cfed5e051a2d41015e300c2bfa9","tid":1280257,"uid":135461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d852f9a58df82dd3be57cf8045dccd90f4f505","tid":1280257,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"仲唔返工？"},{"pid":"19725f92315c7b0c8ac15785f6518aca77b2f444","tid":1280257,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a4ba080fe6fcd7aabefc00a4adcf252728350d","tid":1280257,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"<em>本篇最初發表於一九一九年四月《新青年》第六卷第四號。發表時篇末有作者的附記如下：<br />\n&ldquo;這一篇很拙的小說，還是去年冬天做成的。那時的意思，單在描寫社會上的或一種生活，請讀者看看，並沒有別的深意。但用活字排印了發表，卻已在這時候，&mdash;&mdash;便是忽然有人用了小說盛行人身攻擊的時候。大抵著者走入暗路，每每能引讀者的思想跟他墮落：以為小說是一種潑穢水的器具，裡面糟蹋的是誰。這實在是一件極可嘆可憐的事。所以我在此聲明，免得發生猜度，害了讀者的人格。 一九一九年三月二十六日記。&rdquo;</em>"},{"pid":"bd9d9817ef0318234c3942e78282c6b4a8146341","tid":1280257,"uid":172226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6289604709530983f7ab1fb7cd497772e5305b1e","tid":1280257,"uid":147182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy